{
  "texts": [
    "Functionalities such autocomplete, syntactic highlighting, & actual time debugging have begun to be included into Integrated Development Environments (IDEs) including Eclipse, Visual Studio, and IntelligJ IDEA.",
    "This was the first major action meant to reduce the cognitive load on developers.",
    "By offering pre-designed, flexible components, templates & frameworks such as Bootstrap for front-end development and Spring Boot for Java programs have simplified their development.Still, the major progress came from integrating natural language processing and AI.",
    "From just helping with syntax & formatting, machines evolved to understand context, goal & human language.",
    "This led to notable progress with tools like Amazon CodeWhisperer and GitHub Copilot."
  ]
}